Pickled Quasit				KEY:Discovery ~ Pickled Quasit				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AlchemistClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.AlchemistDiscovery																					PREVARGTEQ:classlevel("Alchemist"),10			SOURCEPAGE:p.26			DESC:You seal a quasit in a bottle, which you prepare for use as an extract. You activate the extract by throwing the bottle at a square within 30 feet, releasing the quasit. The quasit is not under the your control, but is otherwise treated as a summoned creature. The quasit remains for (CASTERLEVEL) rounds. Creating a pickled quasit requires a 4th-level extract.
Plague Vector				KEY:Discovery ~ Plague Vector				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AlchemistClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.AlchemistDiscovery				PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Discovery ~ Plague Bomb		PREVARGTEQ:classlevel("Alchemist"),14			SOURCEPAGE:p.26			DESC:This operates as plague bomb except for the following changes. The chosen disease's save DC is (10+(CASTERLEVEL/2+INT)). Any creatures affected by the chosen disease become vectors for it, spreading the disease through physical contact for a number of days equal to the
alchemistâ€™s Intelligence modifier (minimum 1).. The save DC to avoid contracting the disease from the vector is the same as the DC used for this discovery.
Profane Bomb*				KEY:Discovery ~ Profane Bomb				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AlchemistClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.AlchemistDiscovery																					PREVARGTEQ:classlevel("Alchemist"),8			SOURCEPAGE:p.26			DESC:The bomb deals evil divine damage. Good creatures that take a direct hit from a profane bomb must succeed at a Fortitude save or be staggered on their next turn. Against a neutral creature, a profane bomb deals half damage, and the target is not affected by the bomb's staggering effect. A profane bomb has no effect against evil-aligned creatures.
Tainted Infusion			KEY:Discovery ~ Tainted Infusion			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AlchemistClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.AlchemistDiscovery				PREABILITY:2,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Discovery ~ Delayed Bomb,Discovery ~ Infusion									SOURCEPAGE:p.26			DESC:When preparing an extract with the infusion discovery, you can lace the extract with one of you bombs as long as the extract has a duration greater than instantaneous. If you choose, you can reduce the duration of the extract to 1 round. As soon as the extract's duration expires, it detonates, dealing 150% of the bomb's damage to the drinker. This effect does not produce a splash radius. Producing a tainted extract consumes both an infusion slot and a daily bomb use.

